Changes made during the port:

  * Auth delegated to `az account get-access-token` instead of azidentity.
  * Errors returned to callers instead of `os.Exit(1)`.
  * JWT claim extraction reimplemented without github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5.
  * Dropped: pkg/common (color/error types), pkg/mcp, cmd/* (cobra wiring),
    pkg/utils (token-debug subcommand).
